		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I recently got a new graphics card and desmume performs a <em>little</em> better in Open GL mode now.
<br />There seem to be people developing some kind of filters for N64 emulators that make heavy use of current gfx cards' pixel shader technology.
<br />
<br />Unless you want to experience that, a high-end gfx card really isn't that important. A faster cpu will probably be much more beneficial, especially if you use VBA's VRAM viewer a lot.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


